creator: PointZero Co.
descriptionHtml:
Thank You 7 years anniversary!
A realistic claw crane game is reproduced to your smart phone.
The 2nd of the series which has been loved by more than 5 million players total.
The prizes are cute stuffed kittens that are very soft and limp. Realistic soft feel makes you feel being healed.
Know more about cat species, collecting the stuffed cats designed based on real breeds like American Shorthair, Persian, Siamese and so on.
And, with the variety of various coats of hair, there is total number of 176 kinds. New friends come up every day. Let's aim at the completion of the collection while being covered with cute cats.
The operation is simple. Just press the movement buttons and release them with sufficient timing. Swipe the screen to look into prizes for a favorite angle.
For the ones who felt mortified for having not been able to get prizes at a game arcade. Get as many prizes as you want in this game.

Got the 1st place of iPad App Store ranking in Japan.
Got the 9th place of Amazon App Store ranking in Japan.

For more of our games, please visit our website at:
www.pointzero.co.jp
